## вңЁ Features

### рҹҸҘ Clinical
- **Patient Management** вҖ” Registration, MRN, demographics, photo, status tracking
- **Appointments** вҖ” Schedule, check-in, queue, calendar view, reminders
- **EMR (Electronic Medical Records)** вҖ” SOAP notes, vitals, BMI calculation, encounter history
- **Laboratory** вҖ” Lab catalog, order tests, results entry, status tracking
- **Radiology** вҖ” Imaging orders, reports, modality tracking
- **Pharmacy** вҖ” Prescriptions, dispensing, inventory management
- **Nursing** вҖ” Nursing notes, task assignments, vitals monitoring
- **Queue Management** вҖ” Digital queue, check-in flow, department routing
- **Referrals** вҖ” Internal & external referrals, tracking
- **Home Visits** вҖ” Schedule, assign staff, track completion
- **Telemedicine** вҖ” Virtual consultations, waiting room, chat
- **ICD-10 Code Browser** вҖ” 200+ codes, searchable, chronic disease flags
- **Medication Database** вҖ” 20+ drugs with indications, interactions, contraindications
- **Allergy Tracking** вҖ” Per-patient allergies, severity, reaction, auto-alerts on prescribing
- **Patient History Timeline** вҖ” Aggregated chronological view of all patient events

### рҹ’° Financial
- **Invoicing** вҖ” Create, view, pay, partial payments, overdue tracking
- **Insurance Claims** вҖ” Submit to insurers, track status (draft вҶ’ submitted вҶ’ approved/denied), auto-pay invoices on approval
- **Payment Gateway** вҖ” Stripe checkout integration, payment links for sharing
- **Revenue Reports** вҖ” Monthly breakdown, aging reports (30/60/90+ days), collection rates, top patients
- **Multi-Currency** вҖ” SAR, USD, EUR, AED, EGP with automatic conversion
- **SaaS Billing** вҖ” Subscription management for the platform itself

### рҹ”җ Security & Access
- **Multi-Tenant** вҖ” Organization-based isolation, slug-based routing
- **Role-Based Access Control** вҖ” 20+ granular permissions
- **Two-Factor Authentication** вҖ” TOTP-based (Google Authenticator, Authy) with QR setup
- **Password Management** вҖ” Forgot/reset flow, change password, history tracking
- **OTP Verification** вҖ” Phone/email verification for patient portal
- **Audit Logging** вҖ” All actions logged (login, CRUD, changes), filterable viewer
- **JWT Auth** вҖ” Access + refresh tokens, MFA partial token flow
- **Session Management** вҖ” View active sessions, revoke access

### рҹ“„ Document Management
- **File Upload** вҖ” Drag & drop, 50MB limit, multi-category
- **Storage** вҖ” Supabase Storage вҶ’ MinIO (S3) вҶ’ Local filesystem (auto fallback)
- **Document Viewer** вҖ” Full-screen image viewer with zoom, rotate, download
- **Version Tracking** вҖ” Document version history, change notes
- **Categorization** вҖ” Lab reports, radiology, prescriptions, consent forms, ID scans, insurance
- **Patient-Linked** вҖ” Attach documents to specific patients

### рҹ“¬ Communications
- **Email Service** вҖ” SendGrid (production) вҶ’ Nodemailer SMTP (development)
- **SMS Service** вҖ” Twilio (production) вҶ’ Console log (development)
- **Notification Templates** вҖ” Editable templates with `{{variables}}`, per-locale (EN/AR)
- **Pre-Seeded Templates** вҖ” Password reset, appointment reminders, OTP, invoice paid
- **Test Send** вҖ” Send test notifications directly from the UI
- **Notification Logs** вҖ” Full history of all sent/failed messages

### вҡҷпёҸ Operations
- **HR & Payroll** вҖ” Employee management, attendance, leave requests, payroll runs
- **Inventory** вҖ” Stock tracking, transactions, low-stock alerts, expiry monitoring
- **CRM** вҖ” Campaigns, patient feedback, communication history
- **Forms** вҖ” Custom form builder, submissions, digital signatures
- **Workflow Engine** вҖ” Automated workflows, triggers, actions
- **Compliance** вҖ” Policies, audits, consent logs, breach tracking
- **DR Backup** вҖ” Disaster recovery configuration, backup scheduling
- **Multi-Branch** вҖ” Branch management, inter-branch referrals

### рҹӨ– Intelligence & Automation
- **AI Hub** вҖ” AI-assisted features (notes, coding, predictions)
- **BI** вҖ” Business intelligence dashboards, data aggregation
- **Automation Engine** вҖ” Rule-based automation, execution logs
- **Barcodes** вҖ” Barcode generation, scanning, label templates
- **Data Warehouse** вҖ” Aggregated stats for appointments, revenue, patients

### рҹҢҗ Platform
- **White Label** вҖ” Custom branding per tenant, theme colors
- **API Gateway** вҖ” Rate limiting, key management, usage logs
- **Data Export** вҖ” Export definitions, export jobs
- **Bulk Import** вҖ” Import patients, appointments, inventory
- **User Preferences** вҖ” Per-user settings, locale, theme
- **System Monitor** вҖ” Health checks, metrics, alerts
- **Regions** вҖ” Geographic region management, data residency
- **Print Templates** вҖ” Customizable print layouts for forms, reports

