## рҹӣ  Tech Stack

### Frontend
| Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|
| **React 18** | UI framework with concurrent features |
| **TypeScript 5** | Type safety across the board |
| **Vite 5** | Build tool вҖ” fast HMR, optimized bundles |
| **TailwindCSS 3** | Utility-first CSS with custom theme |
| **React Router 6** | Client-side routing with lazy loading |
| **i18next** | Internationalization (English + Arabic) |
| **React Hook Form + Zod** | Form validation |
| **Lucide React** | Icon library (consistent, clean icons) |
| **Recharts** | Charts and data visualization |
| **react-hot-toast** | Toast notifications |
| **clsx** | Conditional CSS classes |
| **date-fns** | Date manipulation |
| **Axios** | HTTP client with interceptors |

### Backend
| Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|
| **Node.js 20** | LTS runtime |
| **Fastify 4** | High-performance Node.js web framework |
| **TypeScript 5** | Type safety |
| **Knex 3** | SQL query builder with migrations |
| **PostgreSQL 15** | Primary database |
| **Redis 7** | Caching, rate limiting, queues |
| **ioredis** | Redis client |
| **BullMQ** | Background job queue |
| **@fastify/jwt** | JWT authentication |
| **@fastify/cors** | Cross-origin support |
| **@fastify/helmet** | Security headers |
| **@fastify/rate-limit** | Rate limiting |
| **@fastify/multipart** | File upload handling |
| **@fastify/swagger** | API documentation |
| **bcryptjs** | Password hashing |
| **zod** | Schema validation |
| **otplib** | TOTP for 2FA |
| **qrcode** | QR code generation |
| **dotenv** | Environment variables |
| **pino** | Logging |

