## рҹ”§ Environment Variables

### Core
| Variable | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `NODE_ENV` | `development` | Environment mode |
| `PORT` | `3000` | Backend server port |
| `HOST` | `0.0.0.0` | Server bind address |
| `APP_URL` | `http://localhost:5173` | Frontend URL (used for links) |

### Database
| Variable | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `DB_HOST` | `localhost` | PostgreSQL host |
| `DB_PORT` | `5432` | PostgreSQL port |
| `DB_NAME` | `healthcare` | Database name |
| `DB_USER` | `postgres` | Database user |
| `DB_PASSWORD` | `postgres` | Database password |

### Redis
| Variable | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `REDIS_HOST` | `localhost` | Redis host |
| `REDIS_PORT` | `6379` | Redis port |
| `REDIS_PASSWORD` | _(optional)_ | Redis password |

### JWT
| Variable | Description |
|---|---|
| `JWT_SECRET` | 64+ char random string for access tokens |
| `JWT_REFRESH_SECRET` | 64+ char random string for refresh tokens |

### Storage
| Variable | Description |
|---|---|
| `SUPABASE_URL` | Supabase project URL (for file storage) |
| `SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY` | Supabase service role key |
| `SUPABASE_BUCKET` | Storage bucket name (default: `documents`) |
| `MINIO_ENDPOINT`, `MINIO_PORT` | MinIO S3-compatible storage |
| `MINIO_ACCESS_KEY`, `MINIO_SECRET_KEY` | MinIO credentials |
| `MINIO_BUCKET` | MinIO bucket name |

### Communications
| Variable | Description |
|---|---|
| `SMTP_HOST`, `SMTP_PORT` | SMTP server for email |
| `SMTP_USER`, `SMTP_PASS` | SMTP credentials |
| `SMTP_FROM` | Sender email address |
| `SENDGRID_API_KEY` | SendGrid API key (overrides SMTP) |
| `TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID` | Twilio account SID |
| `TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN` | Twilio auth token |
| `TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER` | Twilio SMS sender number |

### Payments
| Variable | Description |
|---|---|
| `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY` | Stripe secret key (sk_test_/sk_live_) |
| `STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET` | Stripe webhook signing secret |

### CORS
| Variable | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `CORS_ORIGIN` | `*` | Allowed origins (set to frontend URL in production) |

