## рҹ“Ў API Overview

The backend exposes **100+ REST endpoints** under `/api/v1/`. All authenticated endpoints require:
- `Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>` header
- `X-Tenant-Slug: <org-slug>` header

### Core Modules

| Module | Prefix | Key Endpoints |
|---|---|---|
| **Auth** | `/api/v1/auth` | `POST /login`, `POST /register`, `GET /me`, `POST /refresh`, `POST /forgot-password`, `POST /reset-password`, `POST /change-password` |
| **Auth (2FA)** | `/api/v1/auth/mfa` | `POST /setup`, `POST /enable`, `POST /disable`, `POST /verify` |
| **Auth (OTP)** | `/api/v1/auth/otp` | `POST /send`, `POST /verify` |
| **Patients** | `/api/v1/patients` | `GET /`, `POST /`, `GET /:id`, `PUT /:id`, `DELETE /:id`, `GET /search/quick` |
| **Appointments** | `/api/v1/appointments` | `GET /`, `POST /`, `PATCH /:id/status`, `GET /today` |
| **EMR** | `/api/v1/emr` | `GET /`, `POST /`, `PUT /:id`, `POST /:id/sign`, `POST /:id/diagnosis`, `POST /:id/medications` |
| **Billing** | `/api/v1/invoices` | `GET /`, `POST /`, `GET /:id`, `POST /:id/pay` |
| **DMS** | `/api/v1/dms` | `POST /upload`, `GET /documents`, `GET /documents/:id`, `GET /files/:id/download`, `DELETE /documents/:id` |
| **Clinical** | `/api/v1/icd10`, `/api/v1/medications/search`, `/api/v1/patients/:id/allergies`, `/api/v1/patients/:id/allergy-check`, `/api/v1/patients/:id/timeline` |
| **Audit** | `/api/v1/audit-logs` | `GET /`, `GET /:id`, `GET /actions/types` |
| **Notifications** | `/api/v1/notification-templates` | `GET /`, `POST /`, `PUT /:id`, `POST /:id/test` |
| **Insurance Claims** | `/api/v1/insurance-claims` | `GET /`, `POST /`, `POST /:id/submit`, `PATCH /:id/status`, `GET /summary` |
| **Payments** | `/api/v1/payments` | `POST /stripe/create`, `GET /link/:slug/:invoiceId` |
| **Financial Reports** | `/api/v1/billing` | `GET /revenue`, `GET /revenue/monthly`, `GET /reports/aging`, `GET /reports/top-patients` |
| **Health** | `GET /health` | Server health check |

